nd heights - something for every gardener. You can plant this mix until the end of May. We will ship your order the next working day. G\u003c\/span\u003eet them while they last!\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e","published_at":"2026-04-02T12:59:57+02:00","created_at":"2025-04-29T08:33:51+02:00","updated_at":"2026-05-12T22:45:42+02:00","vendor":"1 of 3","product_type":"Dahlias","tags":["__label:nieuw","Summer","super-dahlia"],"variants":[{"id":57555312705861,"title":"150 tubers per bag","option1":"150 tubers per bag","option2":null,"option3":null,"sku":"Dahlia Super Mix-1","requires_shipping":true,"taxable":true,"featured_image":null,"available":true,"price":"200.00","grams":0,"compare_at_price":null,"position":1,"product_id":15046514704709,"created_at":"2026-03-31T14:20:25+02:00","updated_at":"2026-05-12T22:45:42+02:00"},{"id":57555312738629,"title":"100 tubers per bag","option1":"100 tubers per bag","option2":null,"option3":null,"sku":"Dahlia Super Mix-2","requires_shipping":true,"taxable":true,"featured_image":null,"available":true,"price":"150.00","grams":0,"compare_at_price":null,"position":2,"product_id":15046514704709,"created_at":"2026-03-31T14:20:25+02:00","updated_at":"2026-05-12T22:45:42+02:00"}],"images":[{"id":75416883953989,"created_at":"2025-04-30T11:41:55+02:00","position":1,"updated_at":"2026-05-06T09:22:16+02:00","product_id":15046514704709,"variant_ids":[],"src":"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0567\/5165\/2954\/files\/dahlia-super-mix-dahlias-fluwel-3592631.jpg?v=1778052136","width":3560,"height":3597}],"options":[{"name":"Quantity per bag","position":1,"values":["150 tubers per bag","100 tubers per bag"]}]},{"id":8356185276741,"title":"Wild Romance","handle":"wild-romance","body_html":"“Come and see, I have something beautiful” was what I read in an unexpected app from bulb grower Smit from 't Zand. “I’ll be with you tomorrow morning around head time” I texted back. When I turned onto the path I saw her standing there, at least that’s what I thought. Among his many new Tulips there was one that was just a little bit bigger than the rest with a truly phenomenally beautiful white colour, while it wasn’t completely white. And indeed, when I walked with Bart and Lex between the Tulips they stopped at this Tulip. Sold I said right away, I want to offer this Tulip to my customers in the Fluwel webshop. Just wait a few more years Carlos, first build up a stock, we actually just wanted to ask you if you could think of a good name for this Tulip. Then we can have her registered. I racked my brains but I couldn’t think of a suitable name for this breathtakingly beautiful Tulip. A few years later Lex told me; Wild Romance, we called her Wild Romance. Bulls-Eye Lex, perfect name. In addition to her romantic appearance there is indeed something naughty, something daring in this Tulip. Her black stamens and that fiery red edge…a Wild Romance.","published_at":"2026-03-17T14:34:56+01:00","created_at":"2023-04-02T09:03:01+02:00","updated_at":"2026-05-12T22:45:42+02:00","vendor":"10","product_type":"Tulips","tags":["Spring"],"variants":[{"id":46455104012613,"title":"Default Title","option1":"Default Title","option2":null,"option3":null,"sku":"T. Wild Romance","requires_shipping":true,"taxable":true,"featured_image":null,"available":true,"price":"9.50","grams":0,"compare_at_price":null,"position":1,"product_id":8356185276741,"created_at":"2023-04-02T09:03:01+02:00","updated_at":"2026-05-12T22:45:42+02:00"}],"images":[{"id":48990018765125,"created_at":"2023-04-02T09:03:01+02:00","position":1,"updated_at":"2026-03-10T15:48:28+01:00","product_id":8356185276741,"variant_ids":[],"src":"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0567\/5165\/2954\/products\/wild-romance-tulips-fluwel-3010861.jpg?v=1773154108","width":2166,"height":2166},{"id":49903173271877,"created_at":"2023-06-21T09:11:16+02:00","position":2,"updated_at":"2026-03-10T15:48:29+01:00","product_id":8356185276741,"variant_ids":[],"src":"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0567\/5165\/2954\/files\/wild-romance-tulips-fluwel-1469201.jpg?v=1773154109","width":2392,"height":2392},{"id":48990019060037,"created_at":"2023-04-02T09:03:01+02:00","position":3,"updated_at":"2026-03-10T15:48:29+01:00","product_id":8356185276741,"variant_ids":[],"src":"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0567\/5165\/2954\/products\/wild-romance-tulips-fluwel-6707595.jpg?v=1773154109","width":2131,"height":2131},{"id":49903173435717,"created_at":"2023-06-21T09:11:16+02:00","position":4,"updated_at":"2026-03-10T15:48:30+01:00","product_id":8356185276741,"variant_ids":[],"src":"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0567\/5165\/2954\/files\/wild-romance-tulips-fluwel-4483469.jpg?v=1773154110","width":2822,"height":2822},{"id":48990018863429,"created_at":"2023-04-02T09:03:01+02:00","position":5,"updated_at":"2026-03-10T15:48:30+01:00","product_id":8356185276741,"variant_ids":[],"src":"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0567\/5165\/2954\/products\/wild-romance-tulips-fluwel-7748301.jpg?v=1773154110","width":2392,"height":2392}],"options":[{"name":"Title","position":1,"values":["Default Title"]}]},{"id":8368840999237,"title":"Beautiful Dream","handle":"beautiful-dream-3w-w-g-e-mitsch-usa-late-season-575","body_html":"\u003cp\u003e Narcissus Beautiful Dream, 3 WW, Grant E. Mitsch, 1985\u003cbr\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\n \u003cp\u003eBeautiful Dream, the dream that every breeder dreams; to breed such a beautiful large bright white Narcissus with flowers that radiate with joy. The American-based breeder Elise Havens, also known as Grant E. Mitsch, has succeeded. What a Beauty, what a dream of a Narcissus. Every spring, the Beautiful Dream, with its enormous fresh sparkling flowers, is an eye-catcher at our nursery. Now I dream the beautiful dream that they grow well and healthily for us and that I can offer them to hundreds of Narcissus lovers in the future. So far it's going well, they have never let us down. Here are the first bulbs.\u003c\/p\u003e","published_at":"2026-02-09T13:18:56+01:00","created_at":"2023-04-14T12:01:37+02:00","updated_at":"2026-05-12T22:45:42+02:00","vendor":"3","product_type":"Narcissus","tags":["__label:nieuw","Spring"],"variants":[{"id":46487246274885,"title":"Default Title","option1":"Default Title","option2":null,"option3":null,"sku":"N. Beautiful Dream","requires_shipping":true,"taxable":true,"featured_image":null,"available":true,"price":"8.50","grams":0,"compare_at_price":null,"position":1,"product_id":8368840999237,"created_at":"2023-04-14T12:01:37+02:00","updated_at":"2026-05-12T22:45:42+02:00"}],"images":[{"id":51407598747973,"created_at":"2023-11-07T15:52:30+01:00","position":1,"updated_at":"2026-03-10T15:47:30+01:00","product_id":8368840999237,"variant_ids":[],"src":"https:\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0567\/5165\/2954\/files\/beautiful-dream-narcissus-fluwel-7578147.jpg?v=1773154050","width":1200,"height":1200}],"options":[{"name":"Title","position":1,"values":["Default Title"]}]},{"id":15677482533189,"title":"Fluwel Experience (‘27)","handle":"fluwel-experience","body_html":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cspan lang=\"DE\"\u003eA Day in Fluwel's World\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003eStep outside the ordinary for a day and immerse yourself in the colorful world of Fluwel. On this exclusive spring experience, you’ll get to explore the story behind our love for flower bulbs and the Fluwel company.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cem\u003eWhat can you expect?\u003c\/em\u003e\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cem\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c\/em\u003e\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003eWe'll welcome you at our place from 10:30 AM with coffee, tea, and homemade pastries. A Fluwel expert will then guide you on a personal tour of our show and picking gardens, home to a wide variety of special Tulips. You’ll hear the stories behind the bulbs, learn to see them like an expert, and experience spring at its very best.”\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003eAround 12:45 PM, you'll enjoy a delicious lunch at our adventure park, \u003ca href=\"http:\/\/www.landvanfluwel.nl\/\"\u003eLand van Fluwel\u003c\/a\u003e, with views over the flower bulb fields.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003eIn the afternoon, we'll visit the Daffodil Show Garden at the back of the property, where you can marvel at the enormous variety of Daffodils.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cmeta charset=\"utf-8\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003eYou'll go home with:\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e🪣 a bucket of freshly picked Tulips\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e🌸 a box of Dahlias to enjoy later\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003elots of fascinating bulb stories\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003eWant to continue enjoying the experience afterward? We'd be happy to give you tips on the most beautiful flower fields in the area, where you can take stunning photos.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePractical Information\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ePrice: €95 per person\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eMaximum 15 people per day\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDate: last week of April 2026 (exact date to be determined; we will contact you)\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eAre you unexpectedly unable to attend? Then you'll receive a €95 voucher for our shop.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cbr\u003e🌷🌼 An unforgettable, blooming day in the Kop van Noord-Holland region. See you soon!\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","published_at":"2026-02-08T19:07:24